\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 Settings for the block editor and individual blocks. These include things like:\uc0\u8232 \'96 Which customization options should be available to the user.\u8232 \'96 The default colors, font sizes\'85 available to the user.\u8232 \'96 CSS custom properties and class names used in styles.\u8232 \'96 And the default layout of the editor (widths and available alignments).\
