\fs40 \cf2 \ul \ulc4 useRootPaddingAwareAlignments
\f2\b \cf2 \ulnone \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 Enables root padding (the values from 
\f3\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf2 styles.spacing.padding
