\f3\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf2 styles.spacing.padding
\f1\fs32 \cf2  should always be set as an object with 
\f3\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf2 top
\f1\fs32 \cf2 , 
\f3\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf2 right
\f1\fs32 \cf2 , 
\f3\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf2 bottom
\f1\fs32 \cf2 , 
\f3\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf2 left
